          "backend/src/main/java/com/demo/sso/config/MicrosoftAuthProperties.java"
        ],
        "evidence": [
          "`ProviderConfigController` decides Microsoft availability by combining rollout flags with `isClientSideConfigured()` and `isServerSideConfigured()`.",
          "`AuthController` separately checks `rolloutProperties.getMicrosoft().isClientSideEnabled()` before challenge/verify and also treats `ObjectProvider<MicrosoftTokenVerifier>` absence as another disablement path.",
