        "dimension": "logic_clarity",
        "related_files": [
          "backend/src/main/java/com/demo/sso/controller/ProviderConfigController.java"
        ],
        "evidence": [
          "The constructor assigns `this.googleClientId = googleClientId == null ? \"\" : googleClientId;`, so the field is never `null` after construction.",
          "`getProviders()` still computes `boolean googleConfigured = googleClientId != null && !googleClientId.isBlank();`, which means the left side of the `&&` can never change the result."
        ],
