        ],
        "evidence": [
          "service/model/ has exactly 1 file (AuthenticatedUserIdentity.java, ~50 LOC)",
          "AuthenticatedUserIdentity is a cross-cutting identity record used by JwtTokenService (token/), UserController (controller/), JwtAuthenticationFilter (config/), and UserService (user/)",
          "NormalizedIdentity, a sibling identity record with a similar role (pre-auth identity vs post-auth identity), lives in service/auth/ \u2014 the split between service/model/ and service/auth/ for identity records is not intuitive",
